1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,400
Kaede? Why?

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:03,400
Even if you find her,
what then?

3
00:00:04,040 --> 00:00:05,600
She went through so much
to get away.

4
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,920
If you know, just tell me
where she is.

5
00:00:07,920 --> 00:00:09,600
If you two see each other again,

6
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:11,680
it'll be just like high school.

7
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:12,840
You'll only end up hurting her again.

8
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,280
Do you understand the consequences?

9
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:15,840
Staying apart like this

10
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,720
is what's best for both of you.

11
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:27,360
So it was my dad...

12
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:28,360
Why?

13
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:30,720
Where are you planning to go?

14
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:33,640
The revenge is over.

15
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,440
Where are you going?

16
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:38,600
We'll only be happy if we're apart.

17
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:42,720
I told you to protect
the young lady's happiness.

18
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:44,240
Can you promise me that?

19
00:00:45,720 --> 00:00:47,200
I can't be
by your side anymore.

20
00:00:47,360 --> 00:00:48,280
Even if Nakama Kaito

21
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,080
hadn't done anything to me,

22
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,120
I was already planning

23
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:51,040
to leave anyway.

24
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:51,640
So...

25
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,640
Wait.

26
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,280
You mentioned Kaito...

27
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,560
What is it?

28
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,400
About the president's birthday party.

29
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:05,400
The guest list.

30
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,440
As you instructed,

31
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,040
members of the press
are also expected to attend.

32
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,120
On my birthday,

33
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,480
on that very day,

34
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,800
as a birthday present,

35
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,800
I'm going to enjoy

36
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,280
the whole scene.

37
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:22,200
I'm going to expose
their relationship,

38
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,560
along with all those

39
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,120
scandalous photos of them.

40
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,640
Right there at the party,

41
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,840
for everyone to see.

42
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,680
And I'll spread them all over the internet.

43
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,240
I'll completely

44
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:33,200
ruin their lives.

45
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,280
After I'm done with Reika,
you're next,

46
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:37,320
Sami.

47
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,040
Us, going on a date like this...

48
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,840
Come to think of it,
I think this is our first time, isn't it?

49
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,200
Hm? Is it?

50
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,080
Yeah.

51
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:52,800
We've always

52
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:53,880
had to see each other in secret.

53
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,080
You're right.

54
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,440
I'm so happy.

55
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,200
Is that wrong?

56
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,920
It's finally happening.

57
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:06,600
It feels so naughty.

58
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:07,840
What?

59
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,160
This is our first
and last date.

60
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,640
I have no other way

61
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,760
to protect Reika.
